<item>
            <title>[LU-11852] osc cache waiters wakeups and skipping queue</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11852</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;No need to wakeup osc_entry_cache waiters with EDQUOT or insufficent&lt;br/&gt;
grants, cause they will sleep again.&lt;br/&gt;
osc_enter_cache could skip queue of waiters if client has enough&lt;br/&gt;
grants, and this leads to new IO happen before an old IO.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
